#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.multiple_of"
msgstr "# triton.language.multiple_of"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:4
msgid "`multiple_of` 用于向编译器声明输入张量中的第一个值是某个数的倍数。"
msgstr "`multiple_of` is used to declare to the compiler that the first value in the input tensor is a multiple of a certain number."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.multiple_of(input, values, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|------|------|--------|----------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | 必需 | 输入张量，其值都是某个数的倍数 |\n"
"| `values` | `constexpr[int]` 或 `list[constexpr[int]]` | 必需 | 声明输入值是这些数的倍数（单个整数或按维度的整数序列） |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | Required | Input tensor, whose values are all multiples of a certain number |\n"
"| `values` | `constexpr[int]` or `list[constexpr[int]]` | Required | Declares that the input values are multiples of these numbers (a single integer or a sequence of integers per dimension) |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:14
msgid ""
"**`values`描述着每个维度第一个值的可除性特征，所以`values` 的维度要与`input` 的维度相同。\n"
"注意当`shape`的最后一维为`1`时出现的降维情况。**\n"
msgstr ""
"**`values` describes the divisibility characteristics of the first value in each dimension, so the dimensions of `values` must match those of `input`.\n"
"Note the dimensionality reduction that occurs when the last dimension of `shape` is `1`.**\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:16
msgid "如：二维 `input`对应通用`values`入参为`[1,1]`。"
msgstr "For example: the two-dimensional `input` corresponds to the general `values` input parameter as `[1,1]`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:18
msgid "### 2.2 类型支持"
msgstr "### 2.2 Type Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:20
msgid "A3："
msgstr "A3:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:22
msgid ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| GPU | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | ×| × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
msgstr ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| GPU | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | ×| × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | ✓ | ✓ |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:24
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions Explanation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:26
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:28
msgid "Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint8、uint16、uint32、uint64、fp64的支持能力（硬件限制）。"
msgstr "Ascend lacks support for uint8, uint16, uint32, uint64, and fp64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation)."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:30
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/multiple_of.md:32
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def basic_multiple_of_example(A, B, BLOCK_SIZE: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    offsets = tl.arange(0, BLOCK_SIZE)\n"
"    input_data = tl.load(A + offsets)\n"
"\n"
"    # 声明输入张量的第一个值是BLOCK_SIZE的倍数\n"
"    input_data = tl.multiple_of(input_data, [BLOCK_SIZE])\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

